    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? You've found it! This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, kept in pristine condition and pampered every single day. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014honestly, it's flawless! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
