    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine Carbon Black. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to eliminate structural fatigue. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. The interior features flawless Nappa leather with no bolster wear, and the exterior retains its deep factory luster. A turn-key example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
