    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional example of a modern sports coupe, maintained to a standard that rivals a vehicle sitting on a showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely devoid of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the controls still retain their crisp, tactile feedback. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full documented history included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every detail, from the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, reflects a life of meticulous, no-expense-spared ownership.",
      "price": 46500.0,
